            <p class="mb-4">Most recently I served as a Research Assistant at IIT, building scalable web applications, cloud-native deployments on GCP, and AI/ML pipelines using BERT and CNN models. I’m currently working on a Robotics & Embedded Systems project at Afila Labs — developing a robotic solution for sewer pipeline inspection using LiDAR sensors on a Jetson Nano Orin platform.</p>
            <p class="mb-4">Outside of work, I love reading about technology, finance & business. Feel free to connect — I’d love to learn more about you.
